de.lambeck.pned.models.gui

Class UndoRedoElementBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lambeck.pned.models.gui.UndoRedoElementBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUndoableModel

    class UndoRedoElementBuffer
extends java.lang.Object
implements IUndoableModel
    Can store the List of IGuiElement from the current IGuiModel for Undo/Redo operations.

    Note: Visibility is limited to this package to prevent external classes from interfering with Undo/Redo operations because the IGuiModelController is intended to write elements back into the model without further plausibility checks.
    Author:
    Thomas Lambeck, 4128320
